- Create client and server folders
- create .gitignore and keep adding files that you do not want to add to git

Client Setup
- create package.json with minimal parameters
- npm install react react-dom
- npm install -D typescript
- to enforce type definition for all our pacakges npm install -D @types/node @types/react @types/react-dom
- creat jsconfig.json with minimal parameters
- create src folder
- create public folder and add index.html there, create div with id root and include script file /src/index.tsx
- create index.tsx, add ReactDOM.render and <App/>
- create App.tsx
